    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 452681.0,
      "end_time": 455272.0,
      "text": "to ensure the safety of cyclists."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 456250.0,
      "end_time": 459525.0,
      "text": "The greenway starts from a Chinese tallow tree tunnel"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 459725.0,
      "end_time": 462900.0,
      "text": "around the National Museum of Taiwan History."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 463906.0,
      "end_time": 468194.0,
      "text": "Trees such as Sea hibiscus, Madagascar almond,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 468450.0,
      "end_time": 473210.0,
      "text": "Indian almond, and Chinaberry can be found along the greenway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 473475.0,
      "end_time": 475996.0,
      "text": "and they provide shades for cyclists."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 476626.0,
      "end_time": 477900.0,
      "text": "Hsuan-hui, let me show you around."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 483750.0,
      "end_time": 487750.0,
      "text": "In fact, one of the best thing about here is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 487275.0,
      "end_time": 490561.0,
      "text": "when you come here to the Shanhai Canal Greenway ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490850.0,
      "end_time": 493735.0,
      "text": "you don’t even have to bring your own bicycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 494200.0,
      "end_time": 497830.0,
      "text": "you can just rent the T-bike, and you can be on your way."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 498250.0,
      "end_time": 498854.0,
      "text": "Let’s go."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 499600.0,
      "end_time": 504392.0,
      "text": "The viewing platform overlooks Sicao Bridge and Sicao lake"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 504875.0,
      "end_time": 508880.0,
      "text": "and gives you the chance to see the incredible sunset."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 509325.0,
      "end_time": 514723.0,
      "text": "The greenway is both significant in its cultural and ecological values."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 517250.0,
      "end_time": 519328.0,
      "text": "When it comes to salt fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 519775.0,
      "end_time": 524290.0,
      "text": "Cigu or Jingzaijiao may come to your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 524500.0,
      "end_time": 529765.0,
      "text": "In fact, there’s a salt field eco-culture village in Annan District."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 530225.0,
      "end_time": 533176.0,
      "text": "So, what’s the best way to visit this wonderful place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 533525.0,
      "end_time": 536196.0,
      "text": "Here, you may experience activities related to salt"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 538800.0,
      "text": "and also understand the process of how salt is made."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 538950.0,
      "end_time": 542546.0,
      "text": "In addition to having a try on washing salt field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 542975.0,
      "end_time": 546698.0,
      "text": "tourists can visit some of the historical architectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 547150.0,
      "end_time": 549562.0,
      "text": "built for the salt production business."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 549925.0,
      "end_time": 552142.0,
      "text": "The docents here will show you around"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 552375.0,
      "end_time": 556988.0,
      "text": "the ecosystem, traditional beliefs and cultures of this area."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 557750.0,
      "end_time": 559350.0,
      "text": "Hsuan-hui, we are standing by a crystallization pond"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 559350.0,
      "end_time": 560762.0,
      "text": "in a tile-paved salt field."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 561125.0,
      "end_time": 562597.0,
      "text": "This pond is called iăm-gēh-à in Hokklo."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 563000.0,
      "end_time": 565500.0,
      "text": "Now they are washing the iăm-gēh-à (Hokklo)."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 565775.0,
      "end_time": 569843.0,
      "text": "The salt evaporation pond has to be washed every time"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 569843.0,
      "end_time": 571890.0,
      "text": "a pile salt is harvested"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 572175.0,
      "end_time": 575373.0,
      "text": "so that there will be no impurities in the salt."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 575625.0,
      "end_time": 578953.0,
      "text": "This circle next to the crystallization pond is a brine storage pond"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 579275.0,
      "end_time": 580299.0,
      "text": "called ĭn-gon-à in Hokklo."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 580625.0,
      "end_time": 585866.0,
      "text": "So you see, this kind of work really depends a lot on the weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 586350.0,
      "end_time": 589733.0,
      "text": "And you see, when it rains, the salt will be gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 590150.0,
      "end_time": 594448.0,
      "text": "But the ancestors had a very good solution to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 594800.0,
      "end_time": 595376.0,
      "text": "You see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 595376.0,
      "end_time": 597242.0,
      "text": "here right behind me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 598245.0,
      "end_time": 599770.0,
      "text": "When it rains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 599770.0,
      "end_time": 600929.0,
      "text": "they can put all dried salt in it again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 601125.0,
      "end_time": 604133.0,
      "text": "so that the dried salt would not be gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 604275.0,
      "end_time": 607218.0,
      "text": "Hsuan-hui, let’s go try shoving  and picking salt!"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 607575.0,
      "end_time": 609590.0,
      "text": "Now, I’ve changed my rain boots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 609600.0,
      "end_time": 612150.0,
      "text": "and now we’re going to try to shove salt."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 612300.0,
      "end_time": 612939.0,
      "text": "Let’s go!"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 616700.0,
      "end_time": 619615.0,
      "text": "Wow, it really takes a lot of hard work."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 620625.0,
      "end_time": 622718.0,
      "text": "After shoving just a few minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 622950.0,
      "end_time": 624377.0,
      "text": "I’m totally worn out."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624875.0,
      "end_time": 627537.0,
      "text": "The salt filed eco-culture village"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 627650.0,
      "end_time": 632675.0,
      "text": "displays many daily necessities you would find in early salt villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 632850.0,
      "end_time": 635296.0,
      "text": "So here at Anshun Salt Factory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 635325.0,
      "end_time": 638461.0,
      "text": "you can really learn a lot about salt culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 639500.0,
      "end_time": 641161.0,
      "text": "And what’s more important is"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 641162.0,
      "end_time": 644639.0,
      "text": "to experience how to make salt and how to dry them up."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 648750.0,
      "end_time": 650187.0,
      "text": "We’re now here at Luermen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 650375.0,
      "end_time": 652125.0,
      "text": "and this is where the entry point was in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 652125.0,
      "end_time": 655709.0,
      "text": "When people want to enter Taiwan or exit Taiwan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 656250.0,
      "end_time": 658938.0,
      "text": "they can park their ships over here in this harbor."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 659475.0,
      "end_time": 663191.0,
      "text": "Here, a lot of business people would do some trading."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 663225.0,
      "end_time": 666250.0,
      "text": "Like they would import stuff into Taiwan."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 666250.0,
      "end_time": 670840.0,
      "text": "Or they can export some Taiwanese stuff to foreign countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 671175.0,
      "end_time": 674267.0,
      "text": "And this is why a lot of people call here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 674500.0,
      "end_time": 677508.0,
      "text": "Luermen, as the door of Taiwan."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 677775.0,
      "end_time": 680293.0,
      "text": "There is a path along the Luermen River."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 680550.0,
      "end_time": 682598.0,
      "text": "It’s a good place to take a walk"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 682700.0,
      "end_time": 684642.0,
      "text": "and enjoy sea breeze."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 684725.0,
      "end_time": 687801.0,
      "text": "We’re now here at Luermen Ｍatzu Temple"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 688500.0,
      "end_time": 690691.0,
      "text": "Before we enter the temple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 690950.0,
      "end_time": 694540.0,
      "text": "let’s take a walk around the tour sites around the temple."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 694975.0,
      "end_time": 697407.0,
      "text": "Just behind me, there is a park with"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 697407.0,
      "end_time": 700309.0,
      "text": "beautiful plants, trees, and flowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 700506.0,
      "end_time": 702735.0,
      "text": "where you can take a walk and take a rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 702975.0,
      "end_time": 704127.0,
      "text": "So, let’s check it out"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 710000.0,
      "end_time": 711216.0,
      "text": "This is Mr. Yo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 711750.0,
      "end_time": 712582.0,
      "text": "Hi, Mr. Yo."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 713350.0,
      "end_time": 717488.0,
      "text": "So what is the best way to visit Luermen Ｍatzu Temple?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 717650.0,
      "end_time": 721298.0,
      "text": "I can show you around."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 721298.0,
      "end_time": 721979.0,
      "text": "Okay!"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 724275.0,
      "end_time": 729110.0,
      "text": "First, I would recommend you to appreciate the Dashanmen."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 729175.0,
      "end_time": 732183.0,
      "text": "And then the architecture of our temple."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 732575.0,
      "end_time": 735327.0,
      "text": "These are all carved beams and painted pillars."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 736310.0,
      "end_time": 737118.0,
      "text": "They are worth paying a visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 737119.0,
      "end_time": 739225.0,
      "text": "What’s also worth mentioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 739225.0,
      "end_time": 743170.0,
      "text": "is the cultural and creative products made by Luermen Matzu Temple."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 743300.0,
      "end_time": 747730.0,
      "text": "The design of lucky charms varies from temple to temple."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 747425.0,
      "end_time": 749409.0,
      "text": "If you bring this gift back home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 749450.0,
      "end_time": 752647.0,
      "text": "It’s   like bringing the blessing from Matzu back home!"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 753231.0,
      "end_time": 755407.0,
      "text": "So if you take this back home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 755407.0,
      "end_time": 756879.0,
      "text": "you should open the umbrella,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 757325.0,
      "end_time": 760853.0,
      "text": "and put it somewhere in your home, but not in your bedroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 761375.0,
      "end_time": 763875.0,
      "text": "So if you’re a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 763975.0,
      "end_time": 767121.0,
      "text": "it would bless you a better academic performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 768200.0,
      "end_time": 769480.0,
      "text": "If you’re working now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 769500.0,
      "end_time": 772250.0,
      "text": "it would bless you to have a better career development."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 773225.0,
      "end_time": 775540.0,
      "text": "So if you come here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 775150.0,
      "end_time": 777678.0,
      "text": "don’t forget to bring your blessing from Matzu back home!"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 781350.0,
      "end_time": 785564.0,
      "text": "The two statues behind me are the generals of Matzu."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 786325.0,
      "end_time": 788675.0,
      "text": "One of them can hear from far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 788950.0,
      "end_time": 791446.0,
      "text": "And the other can see from far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 792350.0,
      "end_time": 795825.0,
      "text": "And these two generals are like the helpers of Matzu."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 796200.0,
      "end_time": 800215.0,
      "text": "They will help to see if someone is doing something bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 802750.0,
      "end_time": 804701.0,
      "text": "There are a lot of surprises"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 804701.0,
      "end_time": 805879.0,
      "text": "waiting for you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 808400.0,
      "end_time": 811880.0,
      "text": "Every year during the lantern festival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 811175.0,
      "end_time": 814109.0,
      "text": "many tourists swarm to Annan District"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 814225.0,
      "end_time": 817735.0,
      "text": "because the firework display here is incredible!"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 818000.0,
      "end_time": 822136.0,
      "text": "We’re now here at Orthodox Luermen Shengmu Temple"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 822700.0,
      "end_time": 824918.0,
      "text": "Now, come on and let’s check it out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 827150.0,
      "end_time": 828110.0,
      "text": "Hi,Director-general!"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 828175.0,
      "end_time": 831189.0,
      "text": "Hi! Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 831190.0,
      "end_time": 831975.0,
      "text": "wish you a pleasant day."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 832225.0,
      "end_time": 836147.0,
      "text": "Could you please briefly introduce Luermen Shengmu Temple?"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 836875.0,
      "end_time": 840141.0,
      "text": "Luermen Shengmu Temple is the largest temple of all among Southeast Asia."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 840650.0,
      "end_time": 844525.0,
      "text": "The statues of deity Qianliyan and Shunfeng’er"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 844525.0,
      "end_time": 847600.0,
      "text": "are about 17 meters in height."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 847300.0,
      "end_time": 848500.0,
      "text": "It’s impressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 848500.0,
      "end_time": 852497.0,
      "text": "Luermen Shengmu Temple worships not only Matzu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 852825.0,
      "end_time": 858702.0,
      "text": "but also the Wufuqiansui (the Plague Gods), Guanyin, and Yueh-lao!"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 859125.0,
      "end_time": 863250.0,
      "text": "There’s also a  Yueh-lao Temple where people can ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 863250.0,
      "end_time": 865682.0,
      "text": "for love and romantic questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 866500.0,
      "end_time": 871132.0,
      "text": "So that the God could bless them with a better relationship with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 871650.0,
      "end_time": 873656.0,
      "text": "The annual firework display"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 873657.0,
      "end_time": 875159.0,
      "text": "is an important event."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 875475.0,
      "end_time": 877985.0,
      "text": "The firework display is impressive"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 878200.0,
      "end_time": 879480.0,
      "text": "and beautiful!"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 882450.0,
      "end_time": 884975.0,
      "text": "Next time, when you come to Tainan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 885400.0,
      "end_time": 887750.0,
      "text": "don’t forget to pay a visit at Annan District."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 888200.0,
      "end_time": 890897.0,
      "text": "All those temples and the National park,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 891200.0,
      "end_time": 894298.0,
      "text": "and also a lot of ecological places to visit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 894700.0,
      "end_time": 897400.0,
      "text": "you will definitely have a great time here."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 898500.0,
      "end_time": 899906.0,
      "text": "So, see you next time, bye."
    }
  ]
}